{"tid":1930465,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"視點31：疫症橫行全球攬炒？污名化;疫症學習;疫情下的國際形勢","createTime":"2020-03-17T14:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T14:29:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f32730eed16b3301fbd1dafc499f5ed88d977a22","tid":1930465,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:23:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-_ZYWIf4iy4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-_ZYWIf4iy4&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB6ZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=c3d20022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-_ZYWIf4iy4</a><br />\n<br />\n【疫症橫行、全球攬炒？】<br />\n武漢不明肺炎出現近八十日，已席捲六大洲151個國家地區，地球上只餘南極洲是淨土。<br />\n特首林鄭月娥是日果斷地向全球各國發紅色外遊警示(兩岸三地除外)，以免白費香港人過去兩個月的心機&hellip;<br />\n多個國家及地區於中國爆發疫症之初，就對中國「封關」，為何最後眾國均躲不過大爆發?為何會一發不可收拾，要全球「大攬炒」?<br />\n<br />\n【香港腳，定TPD－1908？】<br />\n香港腳，正式的名稱是TPD－1908，意思是足癬病1908。早期來香港服役的英軍穿著厚重的軍靴，不敵香港潮濕的天氣而生腳病。到今天大家都忘記了足癬病的正式名稱，只記住了香港腳，亞洲國際都會的身價並不因為『香港腳』而自貶。<br />\n因為疫症，『武漢肺炎』一詞在近期引起諸多爭論。疾病的命名以往來自地名、人名或動物名，名字背後往往串連歷史故事或醫學資訊，例如柏金遜症是由柏金遜醫生發現、日本腦膜炎源自日本、豬流感最初在豬身上發現。有人認為這種命名方式會帶來『污名化』的後果，世衛也在2015年更新了命名指引，避免以人、動物、地區的名字為疾病命名。政治與科學之間可以取得平衡嗎？<br />\n<br />\n【疫情下的國際形勢】<br />\n新型冠狀肺炎發展成「全球大流行」，歐美各國相繼失守，確診人數每日遞增。行政長官林鄭月娥表示，特區政府今日內會向內地，澳門及台灣以外既所有國家和地區，發出紅色外遊警示。<br />\n各國的抗疫措施，如何牽涉到國際關係?國與國之間的角力，如何影響抗疫，國際組織又有沒有發揮作用?<br />\n嘉賓:袁彌昌港大政治與公共行政學系榮譽講師<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【疫症學習】<br />\n教育局提倡停課不停學，年幼學生都要在家網上學習。直播課堂、錄製影片、網上功課，均是學生現時生活一部份。有小學決定延遲考試及暑假，力追學生因反修例運動及疫症而停課的進度。共同抗疫，亦要與時間競賽。但停課帶來更多問題，家庭成員衝突、年幼學生追不上網上學習進度，中、小學留級一年是否選項？<br />\n(採訪：彭德章)"},{"pid":"154697b2ce7dc046fa80605dcaffc3e8616dd4d7","tid":1930465,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e057c41f501ad99af2f8886359dd8a3d645c3e","tid":1930465,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcadb89a374cd6b41cde271faca38a57d6c9bf0","tid":1930465,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c15eebf4e725bc7c22b259b37064019811ef40c","tid":1930465,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afcadb89a374cd6b41cde271faca38a57d6c9bf0","tid":1930465,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}